Pre-Game Insights: England aims to commence the tournament with a victory, while New Zealand seeks to begin the competition on a winning note without their captain Kane Williamson.
England and New Zealand are strong contenders for the 2023 Cricket World Cup, with exceptional players on both teams.
Miscellaneous Highlights: The previous encounter between these teams during the ICC World Cup 2019 final was dramatic, with England clinching the World Cup title in a thrilling Super Over contest against New Zealand.
The Narendra Modi Stadium boasts a combination of six black soil pitches and five red soil pitches, offering favorable conditions for bowlers, including good bounce.
Others: England vs New Zealand will be played on October 5, 2023, at the Narendra Modi Cricket Stadium in Ahmedabad.
The match will be live streamed on Hotstar and Star Sports Network.
